<div id="backgroundbox">
<h1>Daredevil</h1>
<div id="box1">
<h2>Headcanons</h2>
Matthew is clinically blind and even with his radar sense he can't do things like watch movies or tv. However he enjoys theater more than he can admit, catching up on all the latest trends in Broadway. <br> <br>
Even though he is a beacon of justice he has a very self-destructive outlook on life stemming from his depression, so besides him almost getting killed many times during his night runs, he indulges himself in drug usage and heavy drinking now and then. <br> <br>
His success as a lawyer did not make him any less broke, Nelso and Murdock has been on the verge of closing many times in the past, only through the patronage of some of their highest profile clients that they are somehow still afloat. <br> <br>
Matthew has a great deal of respect for professional and amateur boxing leagues, trying his best to never miss a fight if they happen in New York. <br> <br>
Has done very little traveling in his life, at least not for pleasure, seeing that the longer he stays away from Hell's Kitchen the more crime may pile up. <br> <br>
He secretly owns a boxing academy less than a block from where he lives, he secretly trains there during the late evenings. 
</div>
